trans-unit.source: Manages two sets of nodes that are already in document order with no duplicates, and returns the union of these sets in document order with no duplicates.
trans-unit.target: 管理兩個節點已經在沒有重複項目，與文件順序中的集合，並沒有重複項目與文件順序傳回兩個集合聯集。

trans-unit.source: The Current property gets modified when the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.UnionIterator.MoveNext%2A> method sets the Current property to the next node and returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>; otherwise, the Current property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 目前的內容有修改時<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.UnionIterator.MoveNext%2A>方法將目前的屬性設定為下一個節點，並傳回<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>; 否則目前的屬性會維持不變。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.UnionIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions this iterator to the next node in the union.
trans-unit.target: 將下一個節點這個 iterator 置於聯集中。

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if there are no more nodes.
Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if this function initializes the right-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: 傳回<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>如果此函式初始化的權限巢狀迭代器。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the next node needs to be fetched from the left-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: 傳回<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>下一個節點是否需要從巢狀左邊的迭代器中提取。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the next node needs to be fetched from the right-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: 傳回<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>下一個節點是否需要從巢狀右邊的迭代器中提取。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the iterator's <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.UnionIterator.Current%2A> property is set to the next node in the iteration.
trans-unit.target: 傳回<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>如果迭代器的<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.UnionIterator.Current%2A>屬性設定為反覆項目中的下一個節點。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.UnionIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>
